<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#wsjvrnvf">当日[dāngrì]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#ravmprqf">当日[dàngrì]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="#wsjvrnvf">当日[dāngrì]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[at that time;on that very day] 当时(指过去)</p><p>想见当日围城光景。--清. 全祖望《梅花岭记》</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="#ravmprqf">当日[dàngrì]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[on the same day] 就在本日、同一天</p><p>你可以当日来回</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
